== 开发 ==

早在2008年10月，网络上非正式漏出了游戏性短片。Hudson声明称其从[[公共关系|公关]]公司的服务器上泄漏<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nintendo.joystiq.com/2008/10/16/rumor-footage-for-new-horror-title-from-hudson-update/ |title=Rumor: Footage for new horror title from Hudson |access-date=2014-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090725183924/http://nintendo.joystiq.com/2008/10/16/rumor-footage-for-new-horror-title-from-hudson-update/ |archive-date=2009-07-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。游戏于2009年7月的《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》杂志正式公布<ref name=IGNrevive>{{Cite web |url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/100/1001902p1.html |title=Hudson Revives The Calling |access-date=2014-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100324130551/http://wii.ign.com/articles/100/1001902p1.html |archive-date=2010-03-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

== 评价 ==

游戏获得从褒贬不一到消极的评价。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上汇总得分为49/100<ref name="GR">{{cite web |title=Calling Reviews |url=http://www.gamerankings.com/wii/961285-calling/index.html |work=GameRankings |accessdate=March 13, 2012 |archive-date=2014-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140907100138/http://www.gamerankings.com/wii/961285-calling/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]的为51%<ref name="MC">{{cite web |title=Calling Reviews |url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/wii/calling |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=March 13, 2012 |archive-date=2014-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007035858/http://www.metacritic.com/game/wii/calling |dead-url=no }}</ref>。IGN打出3.5/10分<ref name="review-ign">{{Cite web |url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/108/1082344p1.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328011334/http://wii.ign.com/articles/108/1082344p1.html |archive-date=2012-03-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

